B.aa6=new A.Y("Turn a Document Into a Structured 5-Slide Deck","You have a full document (e.g., a proposal or report) that is too long to present. You want AI to convert it into a clear 5-slide outline.","Turn this document into a 5-slide outline. Include: overview, key findings, implications, recommended actions, and next steps.","**Slide 1 \u2014 Overview**\n- Purpose of the document\n- Main topic summary\n\n**Slide 2 \u2014 Key Findings**\n- Most important insights\n- Supporting evidence\n\n**Slide 3 \u2014 Implications**\n- Impact on teams or processes\n- Risks or opportunities\n\n**Slide 4 \u2014 Recommended Actions**\n- Short list of actions to take\n- Who should do them\n\n**Slide 5 \u2014 Next Steps**\n- Timeline\n- Required follow-up","Clear constraints produce a clean, presentation-ready outline.","Tell AI the sections and number of slides\u2014this removes ambiguity.",B.aeU,B.Ky)
