B.aap=new A.Y("Turn Data Points Into a Simple Performance Summary","You have a sheet with several KPIs \u2014 each with one current value. You want AI to turn these into a short performance summary without rewriting the entire sheet.","Create a short performance summary using the KPI values provided. Include 3\u20135 insights covering strengths, weaknesses, and anything notable. Use only the provided values.","**Performance Summary**\n- The highest-performing KPI is customer satisfaction at 92%.\n- Ticket resolution time is the weakest at 38%, suggesting operational strain.\n- Engagement score is mid-range at 67%.\n- Overall results show strong customer sentiment with some operational challenges.","Well-framed prompts guide AI to convert raw numbers into insight summaries without drifting into interpretation.","Tell AI the insight categories you care about (e.g., strengths, weaknesses) so it selects the correct signals from the data.",B.aeL,B.Lc)
B.PU=s([B.aaR,B.a9D,B.aap],t.r)
B.PW=s(["Use numbers to constrain answers: e.g., 'give me 3 bullets'.","Ask the model to show its steps when you need reliability.","Paste raw notes and say 'turn this into an executive summary.'","Add constraints: tone, length, audience, deadline.","Ask for alternatives: 'give me 2 shorter, 1 more formal.'","Provide 1\u20132 examples so it learns your voice.","Tell it what NOT to do to reduce fluff.","Chain the task: outline \u2192 draft \u2192 refine.","Use tables for comparisons; ask for columns upfront.","Ask for a checklist before you start a task."],t.s)
